  "description": "Night Vision Pack for Minecraft without turning off achievements  by. Enjoy full brightness anywhere—no potions needed! Perfect for caves, night, and underwater.",
  "body": "<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Night Vision Ultimate</strong></span></h1>\n<p>Explore the darkest caves and survive the longest nights with this custom Night Vision pack! Designed for Java Minecraft versions, it lights up your world without torches or potions.</p>\n<p>No potion effects needed ❌</p>\n<p>Patched mode:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_d204487b-89f0-47ce-8fde-e46ff8bf36f9.jpg\" alt=\"1\"></p>\n<p>Clear visibility in caves &amp; underwater 🌊</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_f264112f-510d-4394-b277-da42fb4ba450.jpg\" alt=\"2\"></p>\n<p>Perfect for survival, PvP</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_bab4c6f8-1a34-4d2a-9dac-142ede8aceba.jpg\" alt=\"3\"></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h1>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1437619/description_e8469030-a8c8-4a2f-81f2-c4de8b84c206.png\" alt=\"4\" width=\"970\" height=\"14\"></span></strong></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Socials:</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Join our discord&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://discord.gg/mYfhfWtH8v\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><u><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1238974/description_ab71df94-6fc9-41c3-ae8b-b021beb72514.png\" alt=\"5\"></u></a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@NetherSparkStudios\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">✅ Allowed with My Projects</a></strong></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li><strong>You can showcase my work in videos/streams if you give proper credit (e.g., link to the official download).</strong></li>\n<li><strong>You can edit file for personal use only</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>❌ Not Allowed with My Projects</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You cannot distribute through monetized links (AdFly, Linkvertise, etc.).</strong></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You cannot edit and re-share my projects .</strong></li>\n</ul>",
